title: Eddies clinch league title
text:
Eddies clinch league title 
THREE RIVERS – Isaiah Miller rushed for 152 yards and scored five touchdowns as Edwardsburg overwhelmed Three Rivers 65-21 to remain unbeaten and clinch the outright Wolverine Conference football title. 
Miller scored on runs of 30, 3, 1 and 39 yards and also caught a 48-yard scoring pass from Dante Razzano. Subscription Required An online service is needed to view this article in its entirety.
